subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Those who ascribe guard Traevon Jackson’s basketball skills to his N.B.A. father have little understanding of how he transformed himself into a starting guard for top-seeded Wisconsin.
